Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20has%20said%20in%20its%20report%20to%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%2C%20prepared%20by%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20(Agra)%20Anupam%20Kulshreshtha%20and%20Aligarh%20Divisional%20Commissioner%20Chaitra%20V%2C%20has%20statements%20by%20128%20witnesses%2C%20including%20the%20cops%20on%20duty%20at%20the%20satsang%20of%20Narayan%20Sakar%20Hari%2C%20popularly%20called%20'Bhole%20Baba'.%20The%20report%20has%20been%20submitted%20to%20the%20state%20Home%20Department%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Adityanath%20is%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20look%20at%20it%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20details%20are%20awaited%2C%20some%20reports%20claim%20that%20the%20SIT%20has%20said%20the%20self-styled%20godman%20and%20his%20aides%20could%20have%20prevented%20the%20tragedy.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20FIR%20registered%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20'satsang'%20had%20said%20that%20the%20organisers%20of%20the%20'satsang'%20sought%20permission%20for%20a%20gathering%20of%2080%2C000-odd%20people%2C%20but%20a%20crowd%20of%202.5%20lakh%20turned%20up.%20A%20total%20of%20nine%20people%2C%20including%20main%20organiser%20of%20the%20July%202%20event%2C%20Devprakash%20Madhukar%2C%20have%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20self-styled%20godman%2C%20Narayan%20Sakar%20Hari%2C%20has%20not%20been%20named%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20FIR%20and%20has%20been%20on%20the%20run%20since%20the%20stampede%20took%20place.%20His%20lawyer%20AP%20Singh%20has%20put%20out%20a%20statement%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20preacher%20is%20ready%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20investigators.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20lawyer%20also%20pointed%20to%20a%20conspiracy%20and%20claimed%20that%20unidentified%20men%20had%20sprayed%20poison%20at%20the%20event%2C%20triggering%20the%20stampede.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20police%20officer%20Anupam%20Kulshreshtha%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20last%20week%20that%20they%20have%20not%20ruled%20out%20the%20conspiracy%20angle%2C%20even%20though%20evidence%20gathered%20so%20far%20suggest%20culpability%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20organisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stampede%2C%20according%20to%20reports%2C%20began%20when%20the%20'godman'%20was%20leaving%20and%20his%20followers%20rushed%20to%20collect%20dust%20stirred%20up%20by%20his%20car's%20tyres.%20According%20to%20the%20subdivisional%20magistrate's%20report%2C%20the%20godman's%20private%20security%20guards%20started%20pushing%20his%20followers%20and%20some%20people%20fell%20and%20were%20trampled.%20In%20the%20chaos%2C%20many%20others%20fled%20towards%20the%20open%20field%20and%20slipped%2C%20and%20others%20ran%20over%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Adityanath%20had%20assured%20strict%20action%2C%20while%20not%20ruling%20out%20a%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20this%20is%20not%20an%20accident%2C%20then%20whose%20conspiracy%20is%20this%3F%20All%20of%20these%20will%20be%20probed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%20Besides%20the%20SIT%2C%20a%20judicial%20panel%20headed%20by%20a%20retired%20high%20court%20judge%20is%20investigating%20the%20stampede.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720498680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fdqk93dl4_hathras-stampede_625x300_06_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhathras-stampede-narayan-sakar-hari-bhole-baba-satsang-overcrowding-main-reason-hathras-stampede-probe-team-submits-report-6064924%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Overcrowding%20was%20the%20main%20reason%20behind%20the%20stampede%20at%20a%20'satsang'%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Hathras%20that%20claimed%20121%20lives%2C%20a%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%20has%20said%20in%20its%20report%20to%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhathras-stampede-narayan-sakar-hari-bhole-baba-satsang-overcrowding-main-reason-hathras-stampede-probe-team-submits-report-6064924%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhathras-stampede-narayan-sakar-hari-bhole-baba-satsang-overcrowding-main-reason-hathras-stampede-probe-team-submits-report-6064924%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhathras-stampede-narayan-sakar-hari-bhole-baba-satsang-overcrowding-main-reason-hathras-stampede-probe-team-submits-report-6064924%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mumbai%20rain%3A%20IMD%20issues%20'red'%20alert%3B%20schools%2C%20colleges%20to%20remain%20shut%20today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720497907000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-07%2F08%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1720431603-4686.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-rain-imd-issues-red-alert-schools-colleges-to-remain-shut-today-124070900112_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IMD%20weather%20update%3A%20The%20IMD%20has%20predicted%20heavy%20rain%20in%20isolated%20areas%20of%20Mumbai%20until%20July%2012%3B%20two%20rain-related%20deaths%20have%20been%20reported%20so%20far%20from%20Mumbai%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-rain-imd-issues-red-alert-schools-colleges-to-remain-shut-today-124070900112_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-rain-imd-issues-red-alert-schools-colleges-to-remain-shut-today-124070900112_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-rain-imd-issues-red-alert-schools-colleges-to-remain-shut-today-124070900112_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Whatchamacallit%2C%20Thingamajig%3A%20What%20We%20Say%20When%20We%20Cant%20Find%20The%20Right%20Word%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%2050%2C000%20years%20ago%2C%20humans%20started%20speaking%20and%20we've%20not%20shut%20up%20since.%20Sometimes%2C%20though%2C%20we%20struggle%20to%20remember%20the%20name%20of%20an%20object%2C%20a%20place%2C%20or%20a%20person%20we%20want%20to%20talk%20about.%20The%20technical%20term%20for%20this%20phenomenon%20is%20%E2%80%9Clethologica%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ehile%20severe%20word-finding%20difficulties%20can%20be%20due%20to%20serious%20neurological%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20a%20stroke%20or%20dementia%2C%20drawing%20the%20occasional%2C%20temporary%20blank%20is%20very%20common.%20Unsurprisingly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F13825585.2019.1641177%5C%22%3Estress%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20help%2C%20and%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.frontiersin.org%2Fjournals%2Fpsychology%2Farticles%2F10.3389%2Ffpsyg.2020.00338%2Ffull%5C%22%3Egets%20worse%20as%20we%20age%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20can%20we%20do%20if%20we're%20coming%20up%20empty%20yet%20still%20want%20to%20keep%20the%20conversation%20going%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20there%20are%20different%20ways%20of%20dealing%20with%20this%20problem.%20We%20can%20hesitate%2C%20using%20so-called%20fillers%20like%20%E2%80%9Cehm%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cuh%E2%80%9D%20to%20buy%20us%20some%20time%2C%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20the%20right%20word%20will%20make%20a%20delayed%20but%20triumphant%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20can%20describe%20what%20we%20mean%2C%20hoping%20to%20still%20get%20the%20message%20across.%20(Recently%2C%20it%20took%20me%20a%20moment%20to%20figure%20out%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cflat%20things%20that%20look%20like%20doughnuts%E2%80%9D%20my%20daughter%20was%20talking%20about%20were%20DVDs.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20may%20even%20be%20able%20to%20recall%20certain%20formal%20characteristics%20of%20the%20word%2C%20like%20the%20first%20letter%20or%20sound%2C%20or%20how%20many%20syllables%20it%20has%20and%20generously%20offer%20these%20clues%20to%20the%20puzzled%20listener%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20know%20%E2%80%93%20this%20guy%20we%20met%20last%20week%2C%20I%20think%20his%20name%20starts%20with%20a%20G.%E2%80%9DThis%20is%20why%20we%20also%20call%20this%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpsycnet.apa.org%2Frecord%2F1991-14347-001%5C%22%3Etip-of-the-tongue%20phenomenon%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We've%20almost%20got%20it%2C%20and%20our%20brain%20is%20doing%20its%20best%20to%20use%20all%20stored%20bits%20of%20information%20(for%20example%2C%20on%20the%20word's%20pronunciation%20and%20meaning)%20to%20come%20up%20with%20something%20useful%20to%20say%2C%20even%20if%20it%20isn't%20the%20correct%20word%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20this%20results%20in%20us%20making%20up%20words%20on%20the%20spot%20(referred%20to%20within%20linguistics%20as%20%E2%80%9Cspontaneous%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cad-hoc%20coinages%E2%80%9D).%20You%20may%20not%20find%20them%20in%20the%20dictionary%2C%20but%20they%20usually%20still%20make%20sense%20in%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20young%20children%20already%20come%20up%20with%20them%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20put%20into%20useful%20practice%20what%20they've%20already%20learned%20about%20language%20%E2%80%93%20like%20the%20six-year-old%20referring%20to%20a%20women's%20shampoo%20bottle%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Clady%20thing%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.museumofplay.org%2Fapp%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F1-4-article-word-play.pdf%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20language%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20favourite%20example%20in%20this%20category%2C%20though%2C%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSophieRachael95%2Fstatus%2F1115329983210242048%5C%22%3ETweet%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20a%20German%20customer%20in%20a%20Welsh%20pub%20who%20couldn't%20recall%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Ccutlery%E2%80%9D%20and%20politely%20asked%20for%20%E2%80%9Cfood%20weapons%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20but%20certainly%20not%20least%2C%20we%20may%20use%20ready-made%20placeholders%20like%20%E2%80%9Cthingamajig%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhatchamacallit%E2%80%9D%20(for%20an%20object)%20or%20%E2%80%9Cwhat's-his-name%E2%80%9D%20(for%20a%20person).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApparently%2C%20the%20struggle%20to%20find%20the%20right%20word%20is%20real%20and%20has%20been%20for%20some%20time%2C%20because%20the%20Oxford%20English%20Dictionary%20has%20its%20own%20category%20for%20these%20terms%2C%20labelled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oed.com%2Fthesaurus%2F%3FclassId%3D152065%26openAt%3D152068%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cthing%20or%20person%20whose%20name%20is%20forgotten%20or%20unknown%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20includes%2064%20entries%20and%20some%20records%20go%20back%20as%20far%20as%20the%20early%20middle%20English%20period%20(1100%E2%80%931300).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20of%20them%20are%20still%20used%20today.%20The%20last%20attested%20use%20for%20the%20strangely%20evocative%20%E2%80%9Cwhiblin%E2%80%9D%20was%20in%201652%2C%20for%20example%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cjiggumbob%E2%80%9D%20is%20marked%20as%20obsolete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOthers%2C%20like%20%E2%80%9Cgizmo%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cdoodah%E2%80%9D%20are%20still%20going%20strong%2C%20though%2C%20and%20you%20can%20even%20buy%20%E2%80%9CWhatchamacallits%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CWhozeewhatzits%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20they%20are%20chocolate%20bars%20made%20by%20Hershey's.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20threads%20on%20Reddit%20dedicated%20to%20collecting%20placeholder%20words%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FAskAnAmerican%2Fcomments%2Fxax5en%2Fhow_do_you_call_things_in_english_you_dont_know%2F%5C%22%3EEnglish%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Flanguagelearning%2Fcomments%2Ff5zzj6%2Fa_whatchamacallit_in_different_languages%2F%5C%22%3Earound%20th