ing%20high-capacity%20pumps%20in%20low-lying%20areas%2C%20inconveniencing%20thousands%20of%20passengers%20as%20local%20trains%20stopped%20on%20tracks%20for%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20out-station%20trains%20on%20their%20way%20to%20Mumbai%20also%20remained%20stranded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20resuming%20services%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Harbour%20line%20services%20of%20Central%20Railway%20were%20suspended%20again%20on%20a%20stretch%20on%20Monday%20night%20due%20to%20waterlogging%20on%20the%20tracks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlight%20services%20at%20the%20Mumbai%20airport%20were%20severely%20impacted%20due%20to%20low%20visibility%20after%20heavy%20rains%2C%20leading%20to%20runway%20operations%20being%20shut%20for%20over%20an%20hour%20and%20approximately%2050%20flights%20being%20cancelled%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2050%20cancelled%20flights%20(both%20arrivals%20and%20departures)%20till%2011%20AM%2C%2042%20were%20operated%20by%20IndiGo%20and%20six%20by%20Air%20India%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFifty%20flights%20have%20been%20cancelled%20till%2011%20am%20on%20Monday%20at%20the%20Mumbai%20airport%20due%20to%20low%20visibility%20and%20heavy%20rains.%20Of%20these%2C%20IndiGo%20had%20to%20cancel%2042%20flights%2C%20including%2020%20departing%20ones%2C%20while%20six%20flights%20of%20Air%20India%20including%20three%20arrivals%20were%20cancelled%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government-owned%20Alliance%20Air%20also%20had%20to%20cancel%20two%20flights%20(one%20departure%20and%20one%20arrival)%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20source%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchools%20and%20junior%20colleges%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Thane%2C%20Navi%20Mumbai%2C%20Panvel%2C%20Pune%20as%20well%20as%20rural%20parts%20of%20Ratnagiri-Sindhudurg%20will%20remain%20closed%20on%20Tuesday%20due%20to%20a%20heavy%20rainfall%20alert%20issued%20by%20the%20IMD%20for%20these%20areas%2C%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wea