ernate%20routes%20due%20to%20waterlogging%20on%20low-lying%20areas%20at%20Parel%2C%20Gandhi%20Market%2C%20Sangam%20Nagar%20and%20Malad%20subway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai's%20island%20city%20received%20an%20average%20of%2047.93mm%20of%20rainfall%20in%20the%2010-hour%20period%20ending%20at%206pm%2C%20while%20the%20figure%20was%2018.82%20mm%20and%2031.74%20mm%20for%20eastern%20and%20western%20parts%20of%20the%20metropolis%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%2024%20hours%20ending%20at%208%20am%2C%20Mumbai's%20island%20city%20recorded%20an%20average%20rain%20of%20115.63%20mm%2C%20Eastern%20Mumbai%20168.68%20mm%20and%20Western%20Mumbai%20165.93%20mm%20rainfall.%20The%20city%20reported%2040%20incidents%20of%20tree%20or%20branch%20fall%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20report%20of%20any%20death.%20Some%20vehicles%20suffered%20damage%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20civic%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20city%20reported%2012%20incidents%20of%20short-circuit%2C%20which%20claimed%20the%20life%20of%20a%2072-year-old%20woman%20at%20Santacruz%20East.%20The%20lady%20sustained%20burn%20injuries%20in%20a%20fire%20triggered%20due%20to%20a%20short-circuit%20in%20a%20room%20of%20Haji%20Siddhiki%20Chawl%20on%20Datta%20Mandir%20Road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20also%20witnessed%2010%20incidents%20of%20house%20or%20wall%20collapse%20since%20morning%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20report%20of%20any%20fatality%20in%20the%20incidents%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20houses%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20legislature%20were%20adjourned%20as%20many%20members%20and%20officials%20could%20not%20reach%20the%20Vidhan%20Bhavan%20due%20to%20the%20downpour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20took%20stock%20of%20the%20heavy%20rain%20situation%20by%20chairing%20a%20meeting%20at%20the%20Mantralaya%20and%20visiting%20the%20control%20room%20of%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(BMC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeams%20of