id%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFamilies%20of%20crash%20victims%20immediately%20filed%20an%20objection%20to%20the%20deal%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bunfairly%20makes%20concessions%20to%20Boeing%20that%20other%20criminal%20defendants%20would%20never%20receive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECatherine%20Berthet%2C%20who%20lost%20her%20daughter%20Camille%20in%20the%202019%20Ethiopian%20Airlines%20crash%20--%20involving%20a%20737%20MAX%208%20--%20said%20the%20deal%20reflects%20%26quot%3Bweakness%20and%20manifest%20contempt%20for%20the%20victims'%20families%20and%20public%20interest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECourt%20papers%20filed%20in%20Texas%20on%20Sunday%20said%20the%20company%20had%20agreed%20to%20plead%20guilty%20to%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%20to%20defraud%20the%20United%20States%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20certification%20of%20MAX%20airplanes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20deal%20would%20see%20Boeing%20avoid%20a%20criminal%20trial%20and%20instead%20agree%20to%20a%20series%20of%20terms%20that%20includes%20a%20fresh%20%24243.6%20million%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20will%20also%20be%20required%20to%20make%20a%20minimum%20investment%20of%20%24455%20million%20in%20%26quot%3Bcompliance%20and%20safety%20programs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20changes%20at%20the%20firm%20will%20be%20overseen%20by%20an%20independent%20monitor%20appointed%20by%20the%20government%20for%20a%20three-year%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20board%20of%20directors%20will%20also%20be%20required%20to%20meet%20the%20families%20of%20crash%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high-profile%20agreement%20follows%20the%20DOJ%20finding%20in%20May%20that%20Boeing%20failed%20to%20improve%20its%20compliance%20and%20ethics%20program%2C%20in%20breach%20of%20a%202021%20deferred%20prosecution%20agreement%20(DPA)%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20MAX%20crashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Families%20reject%20'generous'%20deal%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20families%20of%20victims%20will%20ask%20the%20court%20to%20reject%20the%20plea%20deal%20at%20an%20upcoming%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20generous%20plea%20agreement%20rests%20on%20deceptive%20and%20offensive%20premises%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20objection%20filed%20by%20their%20legal%20team%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20shared%20by%20her%20lawyers%2C%20Berthet%20added%20that%20the%20agreement%20shows%20the%20DOJ's%20%26quot%3Bdeafness%26quot%3B%20despite%20an%20alarming%20rise%20in%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20DPA%20was%20announced%20in%20January%202021%2C%20over%20charges%20that%20Boeing%20knowingly%20defrauded%20US%20aviation%20regulators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20agreement%20required%20Boeing%20to%20pay%20%242.5%20billion%20in%20fines%20and%20restitution%20in%20exchange%20for%20immunity%20from%20criminal%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20three-year%20probationary%20period%20was%20set%20to%20expire%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20January%2C%20Boeing%20was%20plunged%20back%20into%20crisis%20mode%20when%20a%20737%20MAX%20flown%20by%20Alaska%20Airlines%20was%20forced%20to%20make%20an%20emergency%20landing%20after%20a%20fuselage%20panel%20blew%20out%20mid-flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20launched%20a%20new%20wave%20of%20scrutiny%20into%20Boeing's%20manufacturing%20and%20safety%20practices%2C%20with%20formal%20probes%20initiated%20by%20US%20regulators%20and%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20May%2014%20letter%20to%20the%20court%20overseeing%20the%20MAX%20case%2C%20DOJ%20officials%20said%20that%20Boeing%20flouted%20its%20obligations%20under%20the%20DPA%20by%20%26quot%3Bfailing%20to%20design%2C%20implement%2C%20and%20enforce%20a%20compliance%20and%20ethics%20program%20to%20prevent%20and%20detect%20violations%20of%20the%20US%20fraud%20laws%20throughout%20its%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conclusion%20opened%20up%20the%20company%20to%20possible%20prosecution%2C%20with%20Boeing%20initially%20arguing%20it%20had%20not%20violated%20the%202021%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDOJ%20representatives%20briefed%20families%20in%20late%20June%20on%20the%20proposed%20plea%20deal%20and%20the%20company%20was%20given%20until%20July%205%20to%20accept%20the%20offer%2C%20or%20face%20a%20possibly%20damaging%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20was%20meanwhile%20met%20with%20fresh%20negative%20news%20on%20Monday%2C%20with%20the%20US%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20announcing%20that%20over%202%2C600%20737%20jets%20would%20need%20inspections%2C%20amid%20concerns%20that%20passenger%20oxygen%20masks%20could%20fail%20in%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720480860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fhbjdqobo_beoing-737_625x300_08_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-regulator-orders-inspection-of-boeing-airplanes-over-oxygen-mask-issue-6062926%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20aviation%20regulators%20said%20Monday%20that%20more%20than%202%2C600%20Boeing%20737%20airplanes%20would%20need%20to%20be%20inspected%2C%20due%20to%20concerns%20that%20passenger%20oxygen%20masks%20could%20fail%20in%20emergencies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-regulator-orders-inspection-of-boeing-airplanes-over-oxygen-mask-issue-6062926%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-regulator-orders-inspection-of-boeing-airplanes-over-oxygen-mask-issue-6062926%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-regulator-orders-inspection-of-boeing-airplanes-over-oxygen-mask-issue-6062926%2Famp%2F1%22