ers%2C%20the%20magistrate%20passed%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20BNS%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20go%20through%20the%20section%20in%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20asked%20the%20prosecution%20to%20take%20a%20five-minute%20break%20and%20answer%20its%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20even%20after%20the%20break%2C%20the%20police%20could%20not%20come%20up%20with%20a%20concrete%20response%20to%20the%20magistrate's%20queries.%20The%20court%20was%20adjourned%20again%2C%20but%20with%20the%20magistrate's%20remarks%20that%20the%20police%20ought%20to%20do%20their%20%26quot%3Bhomework%26quot%3B%20and%20come%20prepared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifteen%20minutes%20later%2C%20the%20prosecution%20submitted%20a%20handwritten%20note%20terming%20it%20as%20additional%20remand%2C%20which%20the%20court%20took%20on%20record%20and%20the%20hearing%20resumed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Metropolitan%20Magistrate%20(Sewree)%20SP%20Bhosale%20remanded%20Rajesh%20Shah%20in%2014-day%20judicial%20custody%20and%20sent%20Bidawat%20to%20one-day%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20Shah%20was%20remanded%20in%20judicial%20custody%20after%20the%20court%20observed%20that%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS)%20section%20105%20(culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder)%20did%20not%20apply%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defence%2C%20represented%20by%20advocate%20Sudhir%20Bhardwaj%20said%20the%20charge%20of%20culpable%20homicide%20was%20not%20applicable%20on%20Rajesh%20Shah%20since%20he%20was%20not%20driving%20the%20car%20nor%20was%20he%20present%20at%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20Shah%20was%20later%20granted%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720463220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Ftj8haoio_mihir-shah-bmw-_625x300_08_July_