E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20age%20of%20four%2C%20my%20sister%20and%20I%20were%20sent%20to%20my%20grandmother%E2%80%99s.%20I%20studied%20there%20till%20class%205.%20There%20were%20over%20100%20students%20in%20a%20class%20and%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20tutors%20at%20home%20or%20otherwise.%20Since%20I%20failed%20class%205%2C%20my%20parents%20sent%20me%20to%20a%20government%20hostel%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sudha%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20things%20didn%E2%80%99t%20improve%20here%20either%20as%20she%20had%20to%20repeat%20class%206%20and%207%20too.%20Her%20brother%20and%20sister%20failed%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESudha%20realised%20that%20the%20hostel%20made%20no%20difference%20and%20moved%20back%20home.%20Just%20at%20that%20time%2C%20the%20school%20had%20a%20new%20headmaster%20who%20conducted%20extra%20classes%20and%20solved%20doubts%2C%20helping%20her%20clear%20class%2010%20with%20flying%20colours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20palm%20tapping%20was%20banned%20in%20Namakkal%2C%20which%20meant%20an%20even%20meagre%20income%20for%20the%20family.%20Her%20mother%20fell%20sick%2C%20which%20drove%20Sudha%20to%20work%20before%20and%20after%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20go%20to%20the%20sugarcane%20fields%20before%20school%20and%20do%20any%20work%20that%20came%20my%20way%20as%20our%20situation%20was%20dire.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20cycled%20to%20school.%20My%20evenings%20were%20similar.%20I%20would%20then%20sell%20the%20sugarcane%2C%20which%20greatly%20helped%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20class%2012%2C%20she%20studied%20BSc%20while%20working.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20wanted%20at%20least%20one%20of%20us%20to%20study%20ahead.%20She%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducation%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20grow%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20life.%20I%2C%20too%2C%20am%20a%20strong%20believer%20in%20the%20same.%20It%20is%20a%20tool%20to%20move%20ahead%20in%20life%20and%20to%20achieve%20economic%20freedom%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20this%20time%2C%20her%20sister%20got%20married%20and%20Sudha%20had%20two%20choices%20%E2%80%94%20opt%20for%20higher%20studies%20or%20get%20married%20herself.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20no-brainer%20that%20Sudha%20chose%20the%20former%20by%20trading%20the%20money%20for%20her%20marriage%20for%20her%20BEd%20and%20MSc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStarting%20a%20business%20with%20Rs%202%2C000%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sudha%20was%20building%20a%20life%20with%20Kumar%20in%20Coimbatore%2C%20she%20also%20decided%20to%20attempt%20the%20TNPSC%20(Tamil%20Nadu%20Public%20Service%20Commission)%20exam.%20Wanting%20to%20see%20her%20succeed%2C%20Kumar%20even%20bought%20books%20for%20his%20new%20bride.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC84ChyiAbXy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC84ChyiAbXy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3