th%20Rs%202%2C000%20saved%20from%20her%20salary%20in%202016.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20she%20registered%20the%20company%20%E2%80%98Iniya%20Organics%E2%80%99%20and%20started%20doing%20it%20full%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_432339768_933899508403207_22989637245785898_n_1080-min-1720445753.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Iniya%20Organics%20has%2037%20kinds%20of%20masalas%20and%20spices%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_432339768_933899508403207_22989637245785898_n_1080-min-1720445753.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_432339768_933899508403207_22989637245785898_n_1080-min-1720445753-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_432339768_933899508403207_22989637245785898_n_1080-min-1720445753-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_432339768_933899508403207_22989637245785898_n_1080-min-1720445753-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_432339768_933899508403207_22989637245785898_n_1080-min-1720445753-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_432339768_933899508403207_22989637245785898_n_1080-min-1720445753-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355957%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIniya%20Organics%20has%2037%20kinds%20of%20masalas%20and%20spices%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20would%20buy%20different%20kinds%20of%20spinach%2C%20moringa%20leaves%2C%20mint%2C%20and%20coriander%20from%20organic%20farmers%20nearby.%20After%20a%20laborious%20process%20of%20sorting%20them%2C%20she%20dried%20them%20in%20the%20sun%2C%20before%20powdering%20them%20in%20her%20mixie%20with%20her%20secret%20recipe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegular%20customers%20started%20asking%20for%20sambar%20and%20rasam%20powder.%20Using%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20recipe%2C%20she%20added%20these%20to%20her%20catalogue%20as%20well.%20Slowly%2C%20these%20powders%20found%20their%20way%20to%20more%20customers%20and%20organic%20stores%20in%20Coimbatore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESudha%20also%20attended%20different%20classes%20conducted%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Agricultural%20University%20(TNAU)%20and%20other%20organisations%20on%20ways%20to%20make%20organic%20products%2C%20package%20and%20market%20them.%20Through%20a%20well-wisher%2C%20she%20also%20secured%20a%20loan%20for%20Rs%202%20lakh%20which%20helped%20her%20set%20up%20a%20unit%2C%20buy%20a%20solar%20dryer%20and%20other%20machines.%20She%20was%20also%20able%20to%20hire%20two%20women%20to%20help%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumar%20then%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20join%20the%20company%20and%20support%20his%20wife.%20Today%2C%20they%20supply%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351707%2Fdoon-gooseberry-farm-dehradun-sisters-amla-farming-growing-mangoes-brinjals-tomatoes-lemons-in-hilly-areas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epowders%20and%20masalas%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20over%20500%20families%20and%20are%20present%20in%2025%20organic%20shops%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20besides%20being%20available%20online.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20even%20opened%20their%20own%20shop%20in%20Coimbatore%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20now%20sell%20over%20120%20kg%20of%20products%20every%20month%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20over%20Rs%2060%2C000%20monthly.%20Their%20powders%20today%20include%20sambhar%2C%20rasam%2C%20different%20spinach%20(keerai)%20po