ing%20on%20excelling%20at%20her%20job%2C%20she%20silenced%20all%20her%20critics.%20Girls%20can%20do%20everything%2C%20she%20proved%2C%20rather%20emphatically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Romeeta%20spent%20nine%20months%20on%20the%20ship%20during%20COVID-19%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862-768x511.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From1-1720183862-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355796%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22681%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERomeeta%20spent%20nine%20months%20on%20the%20ship%20during%20COVID-19%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20biggest%20challenge%2C%20she%20says%2C%20came%20amid%20the%20pandemic%20when%20she%20was%20stuck%20at%20sea%20for%20over%20nine%20months%20in%20China.%20In%20March%202020%2C%20she%20was%20on%20a%20cargo%20vessel%2C%20and%20with%20flights%20grounded%2C%20they%20had%20to%20stay%20on%20board%20and%20continue%20working.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20stuck%20in%20China%20and%20had%20to%20wear%20PPE%20kits%2C%20coveralls%2C%20and%20masks.%20Life%20was%20hell%20as%20we%20had%20no%20flights%20back%20home.%20It%20was%20mental%20torture%20for%20all%20of%20us%20on%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20this%2C%20being%20on%20sea%20definitely%20comes%2