%20in%20Jalgaon%2C%20she%20is%20today%20a%20world%20traveller%20challenging%20societal%20norms%20and%20smashing%20gender%20stereotypes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20her%20advice%20for%20women%20who%20want%20to%20consider%20a%20career%20at%20sea%3F%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20listen%20to%20what%20others%20say.%20People%20might%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98You%E2%80%99re%20a%20girl%2C%20what%20can%20you%20do%3F%E2%80%99.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20get%20demotivated%20and%20just%20focus%20on%20your%20career.%20You%20can%20do%20everything%20that%20a%20man%20can%20do%2C%20and%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERomeeta%20shares%20tips%20for%20a%20career%20in%20the%20maritime%20industry%20on%20her%20Instagram%20channel%2C%20which%20you%20can%20check%20out%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fromeeta_b%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Romeeta%20Bundela%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720186990000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2From9-min-1720183673.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355782%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Romeeta%20Bundela%20from%20Jalgaon%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20female%20Electro%20Technical%20Officer%20(ETO)%20on%20a%20Maersk%20ship%2C%20overcoming%20significant%20challenges%20and%20gender%20biases.%20Having%20advanced%20to%20senior%20ETO%20and%20electrical%20superintendent%20on%20a%20UK%20cruise%20ship%2C%20she%20shares%20insights%20on%20building%20a%20maritime%20career%20as%20a%20woman.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355782%2Fmerchant-navy-romeeta-bundela-jalgaon-first-woman-electro-technical-officer-seafarer-maritime%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japanese%20Mangoes%20Worth%20Rs%203%20Lakh%2FKg%2C%20Berries%20%26amp%3B%20More%3A%20Udupi%20Man%20Grows%20Rare%20Fruits%20on%20Terrace%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EImagine%20waking%20up%20one%20day%20and%20being%20told%20that%20a%20fruit%20you%E2%80%99ve%20grown%20for%20your%20family%20in%20your%20terrace%20garden%20sells%20for%20Rs%202.5-3%20lakh%20per%20kg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20news%20came%20to%20Joseph%20Lobo%2C%20he%20did%20not%20immediately%20believe%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20the%20mango%20variety%20was%20rare%20and%20expensive%2C%20but%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20realise%20how%20costly%20it%20could%20be.%20My%20family%20and%20friends%20consumed%20the%20first%20yield%2C%20unaware%20of%20its%20value%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20farmer%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELobo%20grows%20the%20Miyazaki%20Mango%20which%20is%20a%20Japanese%20variety%20known%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F347996%2Frare-mangoes-available-in-india-alphonso-sindhri-mango-expensive-mangoes-summer-season%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20in%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20farmers%20in%20India%20who%20have%20successfully%20harvested%20the%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20variety%2C%20Lobo%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349834%2Ffive-tips-to-grow-fruit-trees-at-home-mango-guava-on-terrace-gardening-indian-flowers-sushma-reddy-bengaluru%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrows%20other%20200%20varieties%20of%20plants%20including%20fruits%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20flowers%20on%20his%20terrace%20farm.%20And%20the%20best%20part%3F%20He%20only%20uses%20organic%20fertilisers%20and%20techniques%20such%20as%20hydroponics%20to%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20all%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20this%20humble%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20magnificent%20farm%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98All%20I%20have%20is%20a%20terrace%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20a%20small%20village%20in%20Udupi%2C%20Lobo%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20farming%20family.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20all%20I%20had%20known%20for%20most%20of%20my%20childhood.%20I%20had%20always%20been%20interested%20in%20farming%20and%20felt%20a%20connection%20with%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20you%20might%20find%20it%20odd%20that%20a%20youngster%20wanted%20to%20take%20up%20farming%20as%20a%20profession%2C%20it%20was%20all%20Lobo%20had%20ever%20wanted.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20wanted%20to%20try%20out%20new%20ways%20of%20growing%20plants%20effectively%20and%20profitably.%20I%20knew%20getting%20into%20the%20profession%20that%20it%20is%20more%20passion-driven%20than%20profit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20my%20family%20land%20was%20stuck%20in%20a%20conflict%20and%20I%20could%20not%20farm%20on%20it.%20We%20come%20from%20humble%20backgrounds%20and%20those%20lands%20were%20our%20only%20support.%20My%20dream%20seemed%20to%20be%20out%20of%20reach%20for%20a%20moment%20but%20I%20decided%20to%20keep%20going.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-1-1719992669.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lobo%20grows%20200%20varieties%20of%20plants%20on%20his%20terrace%20garden%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-1-1719992669.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2