Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20been%20growing%20various%20varieties%20of%20gulf%20berries%20on%20my%20terrace%20and%20was%20also%20growing%20some%20mangoes%20as%20well.%20When%20I%20had%20successfully%20grown%20these%2C%20why%20not%20try%20Miyazaki%3F%20I%20knew%20that%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20grow%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20realising%20the%20monetary%20value%20of%20the%20variety%2C%20he%20treated%20it%20like%20any%20other%20mango%20plant.%20%E2%80%9CBack%20then%2C%20I%20did%20not%20give%20any%20special%20attention%20to%20the%20plant.%20I%20fed%20it%20my%20original%20and%20usual%20mixture%20that%20I%20give%20to%20all%20my%20other%20plants.%20It%20took%20the%20plant%20three-and-a-half%20years%20to%20yield.%20I%20did%20not%20know%20what%20its%20value%20was%2C%20so%20my%20family%20and%20I%20consumed%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20news%20reporter%20who%20was%20doing%20a%20story%20on%20my%20terrace%20farm%20who%20recognised%20the%20mango%E2%80%99s%20worth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20after%20that%20report%20that%20I%20realised%20that%20it%20cost%20so%20much.%20Since%20then%2C%20I%20have%20been%20getting%20requests%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20grow%20it.%20However%2C%20I%20do%20not%20have%20much%20to%20share%20except%20my%20soil%20mix%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20variety%2C%20Lobo%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20variety%20comes%20from%20Japan%20which%20does%20not%20have%20the%20right%20weather%20conditions%20to%20grow%20mangoes%2C%20and%20the%20farmers%20usually%20use%20polyhouse%20techniques%20to%20grow%20them.%20The%20mango%20is%20known%20for%20its%20various%20health%20benefits%20and%20distinctive%20taste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20%E2%80%98magic%E2%80%99%20mixture%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20make%20it%20at%20home%20and%20it%20contains%20nine%20minerals.%20It%20is