que.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-1-1719841061.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-1-1719841061-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-1-1719841061-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-1-1719841061-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-1-1719841061-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355089%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGaurav%20ventured%20into%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20do%20something%20unique.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConsidering%20this%20was%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20farming%20for%20us%2C%20my%20parents%20doubted%20me.%20They%20also%20started%20worrying%20as%20they%20had%20been%20expecting%20me%20to%20land%20a%20well-paying%20job%20instead%20of%20getting%20into%20farming.%20But%20I%20knew%20I%20needed%20to%20take%20a%20risk.%20I%20knew%20if%20I%20achieved%20success%20once%20then%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20sail%20through%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEarned%202.5x%20of%20investment%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20mid-2022%2C%20Gaurav%20eventually%20convinced%20his%20family%20and%20went%20to%20see%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267186%2Fpearl-farming-cultivation-oyster-shell-home-made-pond-set-up-ashok-manwani-kuljana%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epearl%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Eponds%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20He%20also%20attended%20a%20five-day%20training%20at%20the%20Central%20Institute%20for%20Freshwater%20Aquaculture%20(CIFA)%20in%20Odisha.%3C%